    "body": "meeting notes: `_abi_encode` must have at least one positional arg. we should document this, and note in the docs that if you just want the 4-byte selector, you can use a constant - e.g. `b\"\\x01\\x02\\x03\\x04\"` or `method_id(\"foo(uint256)\"`",
